<div class="hacker-task-container">
    <div class="hacker-task-content">

        <h2 class="hacker-heading">Task 1: Income Optimization</h2>

        <div class="hacker-task-description">
            <p><strong>Task Description:</strong></p>
            <p>Maximize reward from a series of orders, each with its own value and deadline. This application calculates the best combination of orders to achieve the highest possible income within the given time frames.</p>
        </div>



        <div class="hacker-task-instructions">
            <p><strong>Instructions:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem;">
                <li>Create an input text file listing order deadlines and rewards.</li>
                <li>Use plain text format and ensure correct data structure.</li>
                <li>Input and output file paths should be correctly specified.</li>
                <li>Verify input data accuracy to prevent calculation errors.</li>
                <li>Run the application to get the output with the maximum reward.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>



        <h3 class="hacker-subheading">Input and Output File Paths</h3>
